    of PNF training technique in the development of hip flexibility ROM. First Annual Congress
    of ECSS, Nice, France, May 28 - 31, pp 458-459, 1996.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">2. DUGNANI S., MAURO F., CASOLO F., GALLI M., ZAPPA
